.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER-CHANNEL-AGE-AVG" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-channel-age-avg \- FEAT-2258 average channel age per peer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-channel-age-avg
.SH DESCRIPTION
Average channel open block height per peer, using short_channel_id block height as a proxy for channel age (FEAT-2258).
.PP
Output: JSON with peers map of peer_id to avg_open_block and channel_count.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
